🛒 Amazon Web Scraper Project

This project is a Python-based web scraping tool designed to extract product details from Amazon and transform them into structured data for analysis.

🔑 Features

Scrapes product details such as:

📌 Product Title

💲 Price

⭐ Ratings & Reviews

🔗 Product URL

Automates data collection for multiple pages.

Exports data into CSV/Excel format for further analysis.

Useful for price tracking, market research, and trend analysis.

🛠️ Tech Stack

Python

BeautifulSoup / Requests

Pandas

Jupyter Notebook

🚀 How to Use

Clone this repository:

git clone https://github.com/your-username/amazon-web-scraper.git


Install the required libraries:

pip install -r requirements.txt


Run the Jupyter Notebook to start scraping.

📊 Applications

Competitive price analysis

Product trend monitoring

Market research & business insights
